<title>USA: Zurn Industries Inc Q2 net drops from charge.</title>
<headline>Zurn Industries Inc Q2 net drops from charge.</headline>
<dateline>ERIE, Pa. 1996-10-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Period ended Sept 30.</p>
<p>			(Thousands Except Per Share Amounts)</p>
<p>				 Three Months Ended  Six Months Ended</p>
<p>					1996     1995     1996     1995</p>
<p> Net Sales			$81,516 $70,187 $164,073 $130,343</p>
